trans-unit.source: Provides access to the property values of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern" /> object using its <see cref="P:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.Current" /> or <see cref="P:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.Cached" /> accessors.
trans-unit.target: Fornece acesso aos valores de propriedade de um objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern" /> usando os próprios acessadores <see cref="P:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.Current" /> ou <see cref="P:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.Cached" />.

trans-unit.source: The properties in this structure can also be retrieved by using <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCachedPropertyValue%2A>, using the corresponding identifiers from <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern>.
trans-unit.target: As propriedades nessa estrutura também podem ser recuperadas usando <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A> e <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCachedPropertyValue%2A>, usando os identificadores correspondentes de <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern>.

trans-unit.source: For example, The <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.DockPatternInformation.DockPosition%2A> property is identified by the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.DockPositionProperty> field.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.DockPatternInformation.DockPosition%2A> propriedade é identificada pelo <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.DockPositionProperty> campo.

trans-unit.source: More information about the individual properties is available on the reference pages for those identifiers; see the link in the Remarks section of each reference topic.
trans-unit.target: Mais informações sobre as propriedades individuais estão disponíveis nas páginas de referência para esses identificadores; Consulte o link na seção comentários de cada tópico de referência.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition" /> of an <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement" /> within a docking container.
trans-unit.target: Recupera o <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition" /> de um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement" /> dentro de um contêiner de encaixe.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition" /> of the element, relative to the boundaries of the docking container and other elements within the container.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition" /> do elemento, em relação aos limites do contêiner do encaixe e outros elementos dentro do contêiner.

trans-unit.source: A docking container is a control that allows the arrangement of child elements, both horizontally and vertically, relative to the boundaries of the docking container and other elements within the container.
trans-unit.target: Um contêiner de encaixe é um controle que permite que a organização de filho elementos, tanto horizontal quanto verticalmente, em relação aos limites do contêiner do encaixe e outros elementos dentro do contêiner.

trans-unit.source: In the following example, a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition> value is obtained representing the current dock position for a control that supports <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern>.
trans-unit.target: No exemplo a seguir, uma <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition> valor é obtido representando a posição de encaixe atual para um controle que dá suporte a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern>.
